## IBF Accuracy Standards Used

| Metric | Formula | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| MAPE | Mean(ABS(Actual-Forecast)/Actual) | Model comparison |
| MAE | Mean(ABS(Actual-Forecast)) | Dollar error |
| Bias | Mean((Actual-Forecast)/Actual) | Direction of error |
| FVA | Model MAPE vs Naive MAPE | Value added by model |

